public class SIFActionList<T extends SIFKeyedElement>
extends SIFKeyedList<T>

Represents a repeatable element list in SIF, in which each item is identifed with a key. Elements in the list that are deleted can be identified by the presence of a SIF_Action element with the value of "Delete"
